{"tid":477934,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"$88 一個即食麵？","createTime":"2017-11-23T13:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T10:46:21.000Z","uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"19673f4144a6d7b8aef04efd19b596196ce1a9c6","tid":477934,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的、kiki伴麵出左隻有牛肉既即食牛肉麵、但賣成$88一個....<br />\n<br />\n士多個post:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ztorehk/posts/1783869001657555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fztorehk%2Fposts%2F1783869001657555&d=tUH45TxwMPEETGpwmd1bUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=50f40f01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ztorehk/posts/1783869001657555</a><br />\n<br />\n部份網民意見：<br />\n<br />\n$88，你估你係台灣麵館賣的嗎⋯⋯真係扣埋舖租、人工都有錢賺嘅價錢呀<br />\nZtore伙記下次呢d名過於實嘅貴貨就唔好介紹比街坊啦！真係得啖笑😆😆😆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊有吹得咁好食, 面底同其他台灣知名拌面比較並無突出, 個醬(辣陳醋)完全唔掂, 一啲都無陳醋的醋香, 只有死辣同死酸, 捐到我俾老豆話做乜買啲咁難食的面......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個湯又淡，牛肉又小，完全唔值88蚊，超伏。之前買過程班長六十幾蚊，但人地好食好多囉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你會唔會試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/214606_0172e6e36a4f2bfdce79fa4ffef31bb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F214606_0172e6e36a4f2bfdce79fa4ffef31bb1.jpg&h=abf1f09f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14c919e119d99b315379a8fb6b068a0108a4721c","tid":477934,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:20:38.000Z","msg":"88蚊有好多選擇 不了"},{"pid":"1a9ffe7940e9cddb0fc68c065ccb5d82db5d6a6a","tid":477934,"uid":35639,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"夠食五個滿漢大餐"},{"pid":"29cde60ae536f278b1b986f0910a152e92075827","tid":477934,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"即食麵上到而個價位真係好難唔比人抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b22f4e29af71a28c664a18e7c933b55715f37d","tid":477934,"uid":11977,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:20:21.000Z","msg":"有88蚊點解唔食碗新鮮即煮既牛肉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ab56b5f181f9f03337d6b3278739fad103b251","tid":477934,"uid":45551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有88蚊點解唔食碗新鮮即煮既牛肉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8fb28717107661dd5a42cefdb3a9d61857b521","tid":477934,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"係日本可能食到個靚拉麵"},{"pid":"a25ff89b70b965b1e2576edf9b922722b2401afd","tid":477934,"uid":31098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本可能食到個靚拉麵</blockquote><br />\n一定食到，喺日本就算支賣 1000  yen 碗都只係 70 蚊港紙左右，而日本無乜邊間 拉麵賣超過一千 yen 碗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77239fc727ce8df153f983d23d268ea8dec1eb64","tid":477934,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T18:35:46.000Z","msg":"其實係一袋五個88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c5a6707aea318b5fec91fc00e4e5972c96f5a6","tid":477934,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T22:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係一袋五個88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係一個88蚊<br />\n其他味先一袋五個"},{"pid":"4deeae9faa7ee626c6085297870df704733e9364","tid":477934,"uid":108090,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T23:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係一袋五個88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n懶醒 仲要加個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得自己好撚醒好撚威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59657bc1a5f1c298a0e30c88d916930e9d7e4362","tid":477934,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T23:34:57.000Z","msg":"你地比唔起就食撚屎啦<br />\n<br />\n叫乜撚野春<br />\n<br />\n好明顯目標唔係賣比你呢d窮毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8be278a9d01de754d6c62a06ac7eb523685686b","tid":477934,"uid":10103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:37:25.000Z","msg":"以為係滿漢御品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ee7b0ad7cb014c67b6ae0b6af4e8115d648b57","tid":477934,"uid":61351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/084226_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F084226_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=89116d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻牛肉麵都係賣40蚊<br />\n我覺得幾好食<br />\n88蚊買到2包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e40667cb8764165654e264cc5376a9f7e01c0f1","tid":477934,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"88蚊去鋸個扒算喇好嘛~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8064466c070f11041c0b828ad97e0daf7729da5d","tid":477934,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>88蚊去鋸個扒算喇好嘛~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743ee8b666aea5df2d707d0a39f1ff45bcf91f38","tid":477934,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"要肉啫 買碗味味一品或滿漢大餐都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16eafe02f15fc1ea4f8c36d1fd9bb1388f540e43","tid":477934,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"真係舒琪?"},{"pid":"cb0cee9f50ad2204ed8ee33689cd500c7a112e3a","tid":477934,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"88蚊拉麵都食到個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893f4c3a6a447efb99687bac3fb5fb78e3e1e0aa","tid":477934,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"佢個椒麻拌麵係好食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但啲人話曾拌麵仲好食"},{"pid":"47a4c6cd0a4609a26bc6e797a45b70c8f2bd5b92","tid":477934,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢個椒麻拌麵係好食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但啲人話曾拌麵仲好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曾拌麵係幾好食<br />\n<br />\nhktvmall $49/ 包一包有4個"}]}